      <title>Don&#39;t forget about the difference between android:windowActionBar vs windowActionBar in your theme</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/2022/03/09/dont-forget-about-the-difference-between-androidwindowactionbar-vs-windowactionbar-in-your-theme/</link>
